    "name": "Necrosaturated Stag-Bear",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Some animals, magical beasts, and vermin contaminated with lingering negative energy begin to rot while still alive, rather that succumbing to the mercy of a swift death. Their flesh withers, making them resemble undead, even though they remain terribly\u2014and painfully\u2014alive.<br/><br/> The stag-bear is an omnivorous herd animal found throughout the plains across Weydana-4. The creatures resemble broad-shouldered bears with a wide rack of antlers. Stag-bears rarely pose a threat unless provoked."
        }
    ],
