                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Twice per day, when a necrosaturated stag-bear would be reduced to 0 Hit Points, it can use its reaction to remain at 1 Hit Point instead. It can\u2019t use this ability if a critical hit reduced it to 0 Hit Points. Each time it uses this ability, it gains a cumulative \u20132 penalty to attack rolls for 24 hours.",
